Cottage Cheese with Fresh Berries

5 min
$3
200 kcal
Difficulty: 5%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow FatGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Snack

Tags:

QuickHealthySnackBreakfast

Description

A refreshing and nutritious snack or breakfast option, combining creamy cottage cheese with the sweetness of fresh berries.

Ingredients

  • cottage cheese: 1 cup
  • fresh strawberries: 1/2 cup
  • fresh blueberries: 1/2 cup
  • honey (optional): 1 tablespoon
